{"tid":1017773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制美國可口可樂！支那廠商竟籲大家喝國產「藍叫可樂」","createTime":"2019-02-11T16:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T02:40:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40dfb45e612e36d16aa897c130c5ab099d805f75","tid":1017773,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"雖然美中貿易戰現處休戰，但兩國間的關係仍緊張。最近還有中國廠商打出「拒喝美國可口可樂」的標語，希望中國人改喝中國的「藍叫可樂」，讓台灣網友笑翻。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpTS3P74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpTS3P74.jpg&h=b8a353d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據說中國福建「慕絲妮」公司推出名為「藍叫可樂」的飲料，不但飲料是藍色的，廣告詞也相當有趣。（圖擷自「只是堵藍」臉書）<br />\n <br />\n綜合報導指出，中國福建一家「慕絲妮」公司推出了一款名為「藍叫可樂」的飲料，飲料不但是藍色的，廣告詞也相當有趣。廣告海報上用斗大的字寫著「拒絕美國可口可樂，要喝就喝中國藍叫可樂，藍叫有力量。」<br />\n <br />\n臉書粉絲專頁「只是堵藍」今天就分享了藍叫可樂的廣告海報，更幽默寫到，如果2020票投國民黨，九二共識、一國兩制後就會喝不到可口可樂，「你只能喝到祖國的藍叫。」<br />\n <br />\n許多台灣網友看到後都笑翻，「放心！祖國的產品不管喝病了喝掛了，保證可以退費的。」、「這不是百事可樂的山寨版嗎...」、「無極限了！」、「這個文案可以來高雄觀光局當局長！」"},{"pid":"f82e06c231a84c01ce35ee2a520bc1f1437cbfe3","tid":1017773,"uid":232594,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"個logo擺明抄百事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e342165b80eadb671d81c1c438bfde1f6a5d440","tid":1017773,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:32:27.000Z","msg":"支那狗尻叫有力量 <br />\n吠吠吠"},{"pid":"6881d9a614db71d2bef9b43212a20fdb912b4bb0","tid":1017773,"uid":28913,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"支那話&quot;藍叫&quot;等於台語&quot;碌鳩&quot;咁既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6564c01e0ed229d5a7c0b319669a4cc9625b411","tid":1017773,"uid":189317,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"「藍叫」讀出來咪即係台語既男人碌尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6e0ad794233b9e7fe54ce21d38dd5e79791abe","tid":1017773,"uid":5990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"懶叫可樂？"},{"pid":"38c035bf6c7e1f441cf7197d5376da1f6b7f0341","tid":1017773,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:06:05.000Z","msg":"等睇爆炸/中毒新聞"},{"pid":"e018d91b2f2dee0ee522a130c023c05374fb8fcd","tid":1017773,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:08:04.000Z","msg":"碌鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3568a95b91ec5459864cb5a7ec3dfb413a650c","tid":1017773,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"懶叫<br />\n懶趴"},{"pid":"aae5048419376de0a74416af9010ef540ada1c46","tid":1017773,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:11:01.000Z","msg":"懶叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ad8442ec1805dce12e5a2d319e296d17a8382","tid":1017773,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"百事多年都抽唔贏可口可樂 <br />\n憑你幾句就叫班狗改飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7ead8d8f425b7d8879cde2872e083a2191424e","tid":1017773,"uid":55568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:35:48.000Z","msg":"藍叫普通話同潮州話賓周一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1056ff7c482ee565c1751da930ea7e7e8241291f","tid":1017773,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:46:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5d5256acd3769524f02b99ed0d560ed632fe1f0","tid":1017773,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:40:24.000Z","msg":"藍叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 